Topic model comparisons

2025-02-12

Takeaways

  • NMF is more stable than the LDA-type models (LDA and keyATM).
  • NMF is able to handle topics that don't appear throughout the entire corpus better than LDA/keyATM.
    • Compare the COVID topic in NMF G7/G20 which appropriately peaks in 2020, with LDA G7's topic 21 and keyATM G20's COVID topic.
    • Other topics related to world events such as Brexit and Ukraine in NMF G20 peak appropriately, while their appearances in keyATM G20 suggest that they've been present since the beginning of the corpus.

Plot tips

  • The plots and the zoom/hover features work best in browsers on non-mobile devices.
  • Hover over time series to reveal the country.
  • Hover over topic labels to reveal the topic's top 10 words.
  • Plot toolbar buttons, from left to right:
    1. Enable/disable scroll to zoom.
    2. Click and drag to zoom into selected area.
    3. Reset view.
